      <title>今年美国商业活动扩张速度最慢</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-23/us-business-activity-expands-at-slowest-pace-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国商业活动增速为四个月以来最慢，标普全球 4 月份制造商和服务提供商产出综合指数下滑 1.2 点，至 50.9，为 8 月以来最大跌幅。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-23/us-business-activity-expands-at-slowest-pace-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 14:09:23 GMT</pubDate>
