      <title>伊朗和巴基斯坦寻求修复关系并承诺促进贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/iran-pakistan-seek-to-patch-up-ties-with-pledge-to-boost-trade</link>
